<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>GNNParticles_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`particle_gnn.pyx`<sp/>module<sp/>defines<sp/>a<sp/>collection<sp/>of<sp/>specialized<sp/>particle<sp/>classes<sp/>tailored<sp/>for<sp/>Graph<sp/>Neural<sp/>Network<sp/>(GNN)<sp/>applications<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework.<sp/>These<sp/>classes,<sp/>including<sp/>`Top`<sp/>and<sp/>`ZPrime`,<sp/>both<sp/>inherit<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>generic<sp/>`ParticleTemplate`.<sp/>They<sp/>encapsulate<sp/>specific<sp/>C++<sp/>particle<sp/>types,<sp/>providing<sp/>a<sp/>high-performance<sp/>and<sp/>Python-friendly<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>detailed<sp/>particle<sp/>information<sp/>relevant<sp/>to<sp/>GNN-based<sp/>analyses.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>GNNParticles_classes<sp/>Specialized<sp/>Particle<sp/>Classes</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Each<sp/>class<sp/>below<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>indicating<sp/>its<sp/>implementation<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.<sp/>They<sp/>all<sp/>inherit<sp/>from<sp/>`ParticleTemplate`,<sp/>gaining<sp/>its<sp/>base<sp/>functionalities<sp/>for<sp/>kinematic,<sp/>quantum,<sp/>and<sp/>relational<sp/>properties.<sp/>Their<sp/>primary<sp/>role<sp/>is<sp/>to<sp/>wrap<sp/>a<sp/>specific<sp/>C++<sp/>particle<sp/>object,<sp/>allowing<sp/>for<sp/>specialized<sp/>data<sp/>access<sp/>and<sp/>manipulation.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>GNNParticles_Top_class<sp/>Top<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>**Introduction**:<sp/>Represents<sp/>a<sp/>top<sp/>quark<sp/>particle<sp/>in<sp/>GNN<sp/>events.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__cinit__(self)`:<sp/>Initializes<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`top`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>`self.prt`.<sp/>It<sp/>then<sp/>upcasts<sp/>`self.prt`<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>`particle_template*`<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>it<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ptr`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__init__(self)`:<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer,<sp/>intentionally<sp/>empty.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__dealloc__(self)`:<sp/>Deallocates<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`top`<sp/>object<sp/>via<sp/>`self.prt`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
