<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>**Introduction**:<sp/>Represents<sp/>a<sp/>Z&apos;<sp/>boson<sp/>particle<sp/>in<sp/>GNN<sp/>events.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__cinit__(self)`:<sp/>Initializes<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`zprime`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>`self.prt`.<sp/>It<sp/>then<sp/>upcasts<sp/>`self.prt`<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>`particle_template*`<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>it<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ptr`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__init__(self)`:<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer,<sp/>intentionally<sp/>empty.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__dealloc__(self)`:<sp/>Deallocates<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`zprime`<sp/>object<sp/>via<sp/>`self.prt`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>GNNParticles_cpp_interaction<sp/>C++<sp/>Interaction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>All<sp/>classes<sp/>in<sp/>this<sp/>module<sp/>leverage<sp/>Cython&apos;s<sp/>capabilities<sp/>for<sp/>seamless<sp/>C++<sp/>integration:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class<sp/>...`:<sp/>Declares<sp/>each<sp/>class<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>&lt;cpp_type&gt;<sp/>*prt`:<sp/>A<sp/>C++<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>specific<sp/>particle<sp/>type<sp/>(e.g.,<sp/>`top*`,<sp/>`zprime*`),<sp/>managed<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>Cython<sp/>class.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`self.ptr<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;particle_template*&gt;(self.prt)`:<sp/>This<sp/>line<sp/>demonstrates<sp/>C++<sp/>upcasting,<sp/>where<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>derived<sp/>class<sp/>(e.g.,<sp/>`top*`)<sp/>is<sp/>assigned<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>its<sp/>base<sp/>class<sp/>(`particle_template*`).<sp/>This<sp/>allows<sp/>the<sp/>specialized<sp/>particle<sp/>classes<sp/>to<sp/>fulfill<sp/>the<sp/>`ParticleTemplate`<sp/>interface<sp/>while<sp/>internally<sp/>managing<sp/>their<sp/>specific<sp/>C++<sp/>particle<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
