<codeline lineno="31"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`from<sp/>AnalysisG.core.particle_template<sp/>cimport<sp/>ParticleTemplate`:<sp/>Imports<sp/>the<sp/>base<sp/>`ParticleTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>from<sp/>which<sp/>all<sp/>these<sp/>specialized<sp/>classes<sp/>inherit.</highlight></codeline>
